videos.headline: Miami pulls off an eight-lateral miracle at Duke
videos.description: On Oct. 31, 2015, with no time on the clock, Miami completes eight lateral passes and returns the ball all the way back for a touchdown to knock off Duke 30-27 in dramatic fashion.

videos.headline: Cutcliffe: 'Seven overtimes doesn't compare'
videos.description: Duke coach David Cutcliffe gives his perspective on the final play of the Blue Devils' 30-27 loss to Miami and how his team will look to move on.
